{"tid":2070237,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：《蘋果》25歲生日會  黎智英寄語︰憑良心去做 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-06-19T03:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T03:52:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"100ef977294af87df8d32e896149243c4c155412","tid":2070237,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:52:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200619/FER2K4EOVS7YS5NHFFXFDRLRCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200619%2FFER2K4EOVS7YS5NHFFXFDRLRCI%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C16E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=587d5566\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200619%2FFER2K4EOVS7YS5NHFFXFDRLRCI%2F&h=4f880f82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200619/FER2K4EOVS7YS5NHFFXFDRLRCI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：《蘋果》25歲生日會 <br />\n黎智英寄語︰憑良心去做 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FTMTHCAJKVRCR4UICZAEIBAQV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFTMTHCAJKVRCR4UICZAEIBAQV4.jpg&h=5f6aecb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽日係《蘋果日報》25周年報慶，黎智英同一眾管理層噚日蘋果日報大樓主持切燒豬及祝酒儀式。何柏佳攝<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》明日25歲生日，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。首一堂同《蘋果》賀壽。<br />\n<br />\n員工：蘋果要有125年<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英、集團行政總裁兼《蘋果》社長張劍虹、副社長陳沛敏、總編輯羅偉光同所有同事一齊慶祝，呢個場合梗要肥佬黎向同事講返兩句，佢話國安法殺到嚟，其實大家都唔知點做，𠵱家要靠大家做啦！佢又囑咐同事要對得住自己良心，「第時要靠你哋對自己嘅責任、對社會嘅責任、對家人嘅責任。」大家聽到呢度即大力鼓掌，佢又不忘多謝同事，話入得《蘋果》打工好大代價，好似唔返得大陸等，之後爆一句：「《蘋果日報》做到今日咁，都係你哋造成㗎！」全場當堂大笑，八方相信老闆都係想搞吓gag，心入面嗰句係：《蘋果》做到今時今日，都係靠一班員工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JO5G6YS4DYAYYAFIOHGZMU2JPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJO5G6YS4DYAYYAFIOHGZMU2JPU.jpg&h=b5d40704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中庭位置舉行聚餐，壹傳媒集團同事聚首一堂。<br />\n<br />\n八方之後同好多員工傾偈，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。「蘋果要有125年呀！」<br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}